      <title>对冲基金将汽油看涨押注降至疫情期间的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/hedge-funds-send-bullish-gasoline-bets-down-to-pandemic-lows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自疫情最严重时期以来，对冲基金从未对汽油需求如此失望，随着美国夏季驾驶旺季持续令人失望，投机者大幅削减了净看涨押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/hedge-funds-send-bullish-gasoline-bets-down-to-pandemic-lows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 20:29:03 GMT</pubDate>
