      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/rogers-rout-a-great-time-to-buy-as-price-war-easing-td-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗杰斯通讯公司 (Rogers Communications Inc.) 的股价较 1 月份高点下跌了约 19%，但一位电信分析师表示，现在是“买入的好时机”。]]></description>
